he sake of Allah, and he is seeking worldly gains.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no reward for him.\u201d The people found that very difficult, so\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40966,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/08\/30\/protection-places-of-worship\/","url_meta":{"origin":1867,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Protection inside places of worship during war","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 30, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, dispatched his armies, he would say, \u201cGo forth in the name of Allah and fight in the way of Allah those who deny Allah. Do not be treacherous, do not embezzle the spoils, do not mutilate,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2909,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/16\/jihad-just-war\/","url_meta":{"origin":1867,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: The Prophet&#8217;s commandments of just war","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Buraydah reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, issued orders to a commander of an army or a company, he would personally command him to fear Allah and be good to the Muslims with them. Then, the Prophet would say, \u201cMarch forward in the name\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33596,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/22\/no-reward-jihad-spoils\/","url_meta":{"origin":1867,"position":3},"title":"Haith on Jihad: No divine reward in fighting for spoils of war","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 22, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever joins a military campaign in the way of Allah with no intention but to acquire as much as a rope in spoils, he will only have what he intended.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 3138 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36394,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/30\/salat-al-duha-fi-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":1867,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Duha: Forenoon prayer is better than spoils","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 30, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, dispatched a company that acquired a great amount of spoils and returned quickly. A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, we have not had a company of our people return more quickly with greater spoils!\u201d The Prophet\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22406,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/04\/03\/umar-fear-allah-civilians\/","url_meta":{"origin":1867,"position":5},"title":"Umar on War: Fear Allah regarding non-combatants","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 3, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Wahb reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, decreed, \u201cDo not steal the spoils, do not be treacherous with the enemy, do not mutilate the dead, do not kill children, and fear Allah regarding the farmers who do not wage war against you.\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1867","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1867"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1867\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1867"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1867"},{"taxonomy":"pos